data.description: Welcome to Luxurious Living in Our Modern Masterpiece! This exceptional 1-year-old brick home, nestled within a prestigious gated community, offers the perfect blend of elegance, space, and convenience. With 5 spacious bedrooms and 4 pristine baths, it's a haven for both comfort and style. Boasting a generous 3-car garage, this property caters to all your parking needs and more. Two Master Suites: Enjoy the ultimate in flexibility with not one, but TWO master suites. The first, conveniently located on the main level, provides easy access and privacy for guests or multi-generational living. The second, located on the upper level, is a true retreat. It features a sprawling bedroom area and a large sitting area, perfect for relaxation or as a private sanctuary. Four Luxurious Baths: Each bath in this home is a spa-like oasis, designed with modern finishes and impeccable taste. Gourmet Kitchen: The heart of this home is the gourmet kitchen, equipped with high-end appliances, granite countertops, and an expansive island. It's a chef's dream come true! Outdoor Living: Step outside to discover a beautifully landscaped yard with a professionally built fire pit, ideal for entertaining or quiet evenings with loved ones. This property offers the utmost in convenience, security, and luxury. Don't miss the opportunity to call it yours. Contact us today to schedule a private tour of your new dream home! It won't last!
